{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":999,"text":"If you want to buy high-quality,\nlow-price cocaine,"},{"time":6542,"text":"there really is only one place to go,"},{"time":9403,"text":"and that is the dark net\nanonymous markets."}]},{"cues":[{"time":13664,"text":"Now, you can't get to these sites"},{"time":15312,"text":"with a normal browser --\nChrome or Firefox --"},{"time":19799,"text":"because they're on this\nhidden part of the Internet,"},{"time":22956,"text":"known as Tor hidden services,"},{"time":25082,"text":"where URLs are a string of meaningless\nnumbers and letters that end in .onion,"},{"time":29799,"text":"and which you access\nwith a special browser"},{"time":32629,"text":"called the Tor browser."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34799,"text":"Now, the Tor browser was originally\na U.S. Naval intelligence project."},{"time":39399,"text":"It then became open source,"},{"time":41304,"text":"and it allows anybody to browse the net"},{"time":43915,"text":"without giving away their location."},{"time":46955,"text":"And it does this\nby encrypting your IP address"},{"time":50519,"text":"and then routing it via several\nother computers around the world"},{"time":54319,"text":"that use the same software."},{"time":57508,"text":"You can use it on the normal Internet,"},{"time":59799,"text":"but it's also your key to the dark net."},{"time":64438,"text":"And because of this fiendishly\nclever encryption system,"},{"time":67532,"text":"the 20 or 30 -- we don't know exactly --\nthousand sites that operate there"},{"time":72975,"text":"are incredibly difficult to shut down."},{"time":76642,"text":"It is a censorship-free world\nvisited by anonymous users."}]},{"cues":[{"time":83268,"text":"Little wonder, then,\nthat it's a natural place to go"},{"time":87610,"text":"for anybody with something to hide,"},{"time":89546,"text":"and that something, of course,\nneed not be illegal."},{"time":94799,"text":"On the dark net, you will find"},{"time":96662,"text":"whistle-blower sites, The New Yorker."},{"time":99225,"text":"You will find political activism blogs."},{"time":101735,"text":"You will find libraries of pirated books."},{"time":104867,"text":"But you'll also find the drugs markets,"},{"time":108514,"text":"illegal pornography,\ncommercial hacking services,"},{"time":112643,"text":"and much more besides."},{"time":114264,"text":"Now, the dark net is one of the most\ninteresting, exciting places"},{"time":120098,"text":"anywhere on the net."},{"time":121799,"text":"And the reason is, because\nalthough innovation, of course,"},{"time":125499,"text":"takes place in big businesses,"},{"time":127799,"text":"takes place in world-class universities,"},{"time":130222,"text":"it also takes place in the fringes,"},{"time":132799,"text":"because those on the fringes --\nthe pariahs, the outcasts --"},{"time":137366,"text":"they're often the most creative,\nbecause they have to be."},{"time":141619,"text":"In this part of the Internet,"},{"time":144076,"text":"you will not find a single lolcat,"},{"time":146379,"text":"a single pop-up advert anywhere."},{"time":149449,"text":"And that's one of the reasons why I think"},{"time":151886,"text":"many of you here will be\non the dark net fairly soon."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155599,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":158177,"text":"Not that I'm suggesting\nanyone in this audience would use it"},{"time":161493,"text":"to go and procure high-quality narcotics."},{"time":164405,"text":"But let's say for a moment that you were."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166414,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":168440,"text":"Bear with me."},{"time":170868,"text":"The first thing you will notice\non signing up to one of these sites"},{"time":175468,"text":"is how familiar it looks."},{"time":178299,"text":"Every single product --"},{"time":181289,"text":"thousands of products --"},{"time":183177,"text":"has a glossy, high-res image,"},{"time":187217,"text":"a detailed product description, a price."},{"time":190414,"text":"There's a \"Proceed to checkout\" icon."},{"time":193518,"text":"There is even, most beautifully of all,"},{"time":196300,"text":"a \"Report this item\" button."}]},{"cues":[{"time":198482,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":201213,"text":"Incredible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203163,"text":"You browse through the site,\nyou make your choice,"},{"time":205574,"text":"you pay with the crypto-currency bitcoin,"},{"time":208017,"text":"you enter an address -- \npreferably not your home address --"},{"time":211070,"text":"and you wait for your product\nto arrive in the post,"},{"time":213799,"text":"which it nearly always does."},{"time":217281,"text":"And the reason it does\nis not because of the clever encryption."},{"time":221163,"text":"That's important."},{"time":222674,"text":"Something far simpler than that."},{"time":226027,"text":"It's the user reviews."}]},{"cues":[{"time":227944,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":229283,"text":"You see, every single vendor\non these sites"},{"time":233078,"text":"uses a pseudonym, naturally enough,"},{"time":235420,"text":"but they keep the same pseudonym\nto build up a reputation."},{"time":239610,"text":"And because it's easy for the buyer\nto change allegiance whenever they want,"},{"time":244934,"text":"the only way of trusting a vendor"},{"time":249231,"text":"is if they have a good history\nof positive feedback"},{"time":252893,"text":"from other users of the site."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255396,"text":"And this introduction\nof competition and choice"},{"time":259897,"text":"does exactly what\nthe economists would predict."},{"time":265346,"text":"Prices tend to go down,\nproduct quality tends to go up,"},{"time":270056,"text":"and the vendors are attentive,"},{"time":272453,"text":"they're polite, they're consumer-centric,"},{"time":274908,"text":"offering you all manner\nof special deals, one-offs,"},{"time":279244,"text":"buy-one-get-one-frees, free delivery,"},{"time":282439,"text":"to keep you happy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":284953,"text":"I spoke to Drugsheaven."},{"time":287895,"text":"Drugsheaven was offering\nexcellent and consistent marijuana"},{"time":293809,"text":"at a reasonable price."},{"time":296154,"text":"He had a very generous refund policy,"},{"time":299987,"text":"detailed T's and C's,"},{"time":301799,"text":"and good shipping times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":303608,"text":"\"Dear Drugsheaven,\" I wrote,"},{"time":305893,"text":"via the internal emailing system\nthat's also encrypted, of course."},{"time":310397,"text":"\"I'm new here. Do you mind\nif I buy just one gram of marijuana?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":315450,"text":"A couple of hours later, I get a reply."},{"time":317598,"text":"They always reply."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319230,"text":"\"Hi there, thanks for your email."},{"time":322154,"text":"Starting small is a wise thing to do.\nI would, too, if I were you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":327446,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":329232,"text":"\"So no problem if you'd like to start\nwith just one gram."},{"time":332377,"text":"I do hope we can do business together."},{"time":334912,"text":"Best wishes, Drugsheaven.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":336799,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":338799,"text":"I don't know why he had a posh\nEnglish accent, but I assume he did."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344279,"text":"Now, this kind\nof consumer-centric attitude"},{"time":348799,"text":"is the reason why, when I reviewed\n120,000 pieces of feedback"},{"time":354259,"text":"that had been left on one of these sites\nover a three-month period,"},{"time":358263,"text":"95 percent of them were five out of five."},{"time":362563,"text":"The customer, you see, is king."},{"time":365799,"text":"But what does that mean?"},{"time":367033,"text":"Well, on the one hand,"},{"time":368998,"text":"that means there are more drugs,\nmore available, more easily,"},{"time":373056,"text":"to more people."},{"time":374799,"text":"And by my reckoning,\nthat is not a good thing."},{"time":378799,"text":"But, on the other hand,\nif you are going to take drugs,"},{"time":382536,"text":"you have a reasonably good way"},{"time":385621,"text":"of guaranteeing a certain level\nof purity and quality,"},{"time":390059,"text":"which is incredibly important\nif you're taking drugs."},{"time":393799,"text":"And you can do so\nfrom the comfort of your own home,"},{"time":396941,"text":"without the risks associated\nwith buying on the streets."}]},{"cues":[{"time":401961,"text":"Now, as I said,"},{"time":403461,"text":"you've got to be creative and innovative\nto survive in this marketplace."},{"time":408277,"text":"And the 20 or so sites\nthat are currently in operation --"},{"time":411395,"text":"by the way, they don't always work,\nthey're not always perfect;"},{"time":415124,"text":"the site that I showed you\nwas shut down 18 months ago,"},{"time":417750,"text":"but not before it had turned\nover a billion dollars' worth of trade."},{"time":425470,"text":"But these markets,"},{"time":426647,"text":"because of the difficult conditions\nin which they are operating,"},{"time":429733,"text":"the inhospitable conditions,"},{"time":431245,"text":"are always innovating, always\nthinking of ways of getting smarter,"},{"time":434617,"text":"more decentralized, harder to censor,"},{"time":436879,"text":"and more customer-friendly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":440346,"text":"Let's take the payment system."},{"time":442383,"text":"You don't pay with your credit card,"},{"time":444205,"text":"of course -- that would lead\ndirectly back to you."},{"time":446574,"text":"So you use the crypto-currency bitcoin,"},{"time":448575,"text":"which is easily exchanged\nfor real-world currencies"},{"time":453054,"text":"and gives quite a high degree\nof anonymity to its users."}]},{"cues":[{"time":457367,"text":"But at the beginning of these sites,\npeople noticed a flaw."},{"time":460318,"text":"Some of the unscrupulous dealers\nwere running away with peoples' bitcoin"},{"time":464407,"text":"before they'd mailed the drugs out."},{"time":467155,"text":"The community came up with a solution,\ncalled multi-signature escrow payments."},{"time":475135,"text":"So on purchasing my item,"},{"time":478652,"text":"I would send my bitcoin"},{"time":481702,"text":"to a neutral, secure third digital wallet."},{"time":486799,"text":"The vendor, who would see\nthat I'd sent it,"},{"time":489412,"text":"would be confident that they\ncould then send the product to me,"},{"time":492392,"text":"and then when I received it,"},{"time":493799,"text":"at least two of the three people\nengaged in the transaction --"},{"time":496799,"text":"vendor, buyer, site administrator --"},{"time":499363,"text":"would have to sign the transaction off"},{"time":501799,"text":"with a unique digital signature,"},{"time":503901,"text":"and then the money would be transferred."}]},{"cues":[{"time":506263,"text":"Brilliant!"},{"time":507587,"text":"Elegant."},{"time":508762,"text":"It works."}]},{"cues":[{"time":510877,"text":"But then they realized there was\na problem with bitcoin,"},{"time":513552,"text":"because every bitcoin transaction"},{"time":515277,"text":"is actually recorded publicly\nin a public ledger."},{"time":517799,"text":"So if you're clever, you can try\nand work out who's behind them."},{"time":521100,"text":"So they came up with a tumbling service."},{"time":524409,"text":"Hundreds of people send\ntheir bitcoin into one address,"},{"time":527824,"text":"they're tumbled and jumbled up,"},{"time":529823,"text":"and then the right amount\nis sent on to the right recipients,"},{"time":533637,"text":"but they're different bitcoins:"},{"time":535483,"text":"micro-laundering systems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":537197,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":538755,"text":"It's incredible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":539935,"text":"Interested in what drugs are trending\nright now on the dark net markets?"},{"time":545152,"text":"Check Grams, the search engine."},{"time":547253,"text":"You can even buy some advertising space."}]},{"cues":[{"time":549442,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":551531,"text":"Are you an ethical consumer worried\nabout what the drugs industry is doing?"},{"time":557064,"text":"Yeah."},{"time":558592,"text":"One vendor will offer you\nfair trade organic cocaine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":562010,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":563176,"text":"That's not being sourced\nfrom Colombian druglords,"},{"time":566495,"text":"but Guatemalan farmers."},{"time":567948,"text":"They even promised to reinvest\n20 percent of any profits"},{"time":571284,"text":"into local education programs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":573098,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":574144,"text":"There's even a mystery shopper."}]},{"cues":[{"time":576936,"text":"Now, whatever you think\nabout the morality of these sites --"},{"time":580344,"text":"and I submit that it's not\nactually an easy question --"},{"time":583683,"text":"the creation of functioning,\ncompetitive, anonymous markets,"},{"time":589209,"text":"where nobody knows who anybody else is,"},{"time":591799,"text":"constantly at risk of being shut down\nby the authorities,"},{"time":594922,"text":"is a staggering achievement,"},{"time":597480,"text":"a phenomenal achievement."},{"time":600579,"text":"And it's that kind of innovation"},{"time":604017,"text":"that's why those on the fringes"},{"time":606799,"text":"are often the harbingers\nof what is to come."}]},{"cues":[{"time":610360,"text":"It's easy to forget"},{"time":612488,"text":"that because of its short life,"},{"time":614574,"text":"the Internet has actually\nchanged many times"},{"time":618245,"text":"over the last 30 years or so."},{"time":619799,"text":"It started in the '70s\nas a military project,"},{"time":622799,"text":"morphed in the 1980s\nto an academic network,"},{"time":626799,"text":"co-opted by commercial\ncompanies in the '90s,"},{"time":629285,"text":"and then invaded by all of us\nvia social media in the noughties,"},{"time":632764,"text":"but I think it's going to change again."},{"time":635179,"text":"And I think things\nlike the dark net markets --"},{"time":637799,"text":"creative, secure, difficult to censor --"},{"time":641799,"text":"I think that's the future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":644929,"text":"And the reason it's the future"},{"time":646581,"text":"is because we're all worried\nabout our privacy."},{"time":649273,"text":"Surveys consistently show\nconcerns about privacy."},{"time":652522,"text":"The more time we spend online,\nthe more we worry about them,"},{"time":656505,"text":"and those surveys show\nour worries are growing."},{"time":658799,"text":"We're worried about\nwhat happens to our data."},{"time":660939,"text":"We're worried about\nwho might be watching us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":663072,"text":"Since the revelations from Edward Snowden,"},{"time":665664,"text":"there's been a huge increase\nin the number of people"},{"time":668134,"text":"using various privacy-enhancing tools."},{"time":671250,"text":"There are now between two\nand three million daily users"},{"time":674511,"text":"of the Tor browser,"},{"time":675810,"text":"the majority of which use\nis perfectly legitimate,"},{"time":681001,"text":"sometimes even mundane."},{"time":683658,"text":"And there are hundreds of activists\naround the world"},{"time":686833,"text":"working on techniques and tools\nto keep you private online --"},{"time":693111,"text":"default encrypted messaging services."},{"time":695616,"text":"Ethereum, which is a project\nwhich tries to link up"},{"time":699663,"text":"the connected but unused hard drives\nof millions of computers around the world,"},{"time":704765,"text":"to create a sort of distributed Internet\nthat no one really controls."},{"time":708660,"text":"Now, we've had distributed\ncomputing before, of course."},{"time":711577,"text":"We use it for everything from Skype\nto the search for extraterrestrial life."},{"time":715799,"text":"But you add distributed computing\nand powerful encryption --"},{"time":720312,"text":"that's very, very hard\nto censor and control."},{"time":724625,"text":"Another called MaidSafe\nworks on similar principles."},{"time":727462,"text":"Another called Twister,\nand so on and so on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":731396,"text":"And here's the thing --"},{"time":733410,"text":"the more of us join,"},{"time":734898,"text":"the more interesting those sites become,"},{"time":737373,"text":"and then the more of us join, and so on."},{"time":740268,"text":"And I think that's what's going to happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":742317,"text":"In fact, it's already happening."},{"time":744489,"text":"The dark net is no longer\na den for dealers"},{"time":748389,"text":"and a hideout for whistle-blowers."},{"time":750980,"text":"It's already going mainstream."},{"time":753698,"text":"Just recently, the musician Aphex Twin\nreleased his album as a dark net site."},{"time":760296,"text":"Facebook has started a dark net site."},{"time":764273,"text":"A group of London architects\nhave opened a dark net site"},{"time":767930,"text":"for people worried\nabout regeneration projects."},{"time":770799,"text":"Yes, the dark net is going mainstream,"},{"time":773396,"text":"and I predict that fairly soon,\nevery social media company,"},{"time":777037,"text":"every major news outlet,"},{"time":778496,"text":"and therefore most of you\nin this audience,"},{"time":781604,"text":"will be using the dark net, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":784942,"text":"So the Internet is about to get\nmore interesting,"},{"time":787995,"text":"more exciting, more innovative,"},{"time":790799,"text":"more terrible,"},{"time":792548,"text":"more destructive."},{"time":795140,"text":"That's good news\nif you care about liberty."},{"time":797437,"text":"It's good news if you care about freedom."},{"time":799431,"text":"It's good news if you care\nabout democracy."},{"time":801574,"text":"It's also good news"},{"time":802976,"text":"if you want to browse\nfor illegal pornography"},{"time":805446,"text":"and if you want to buy and sell drugs"},{"time":807799,"text":"with impunity."},{"time":809876,"text":"Neither entirely dark, nor entirely light."},{"time":813799,"text":"It's not one side or the other\nthat's going to win out, but both."}]},{"cues":[{"time":818352,"text":"Thank you very much, indeed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":820240,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}